        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Released version 3.5.2]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The version <code>3.5.2</code> has been released today on <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-jwt-login" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="">WordPress</a>.</p>
<p>This update adds <code>iss</code> support to the JWT payload, tightens revoked token enforcement, and fixes several bugs.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="new-features">New Features<a href="https://simplejwtlogin.com/releases/simple-jwt-login-release-3.5.2#new-features" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to New Features" title="Direct link to New Features" translate="no">​</a></h2>
