</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes<a href="https://simplejwtlogin.com/releases/simple-jwt-login-release-3.5.2#bug-fixes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Bug Fixes" title="Direct link to Bug Fixes" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">Fix: user could change their password using a revoked JWT</li>
<li class="">Fix: protected endpoints could be accessed with a revoked token <a href="https://github.com/nicumicle/simple-jwt-login/issues/75" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="">#75</a></li>
<li class="">Fix user meta not being saved correctly on user registration <a href="https://github.com/nicumicle/simple-jwt-login/issues/86" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="">#86</a></li>
<li class="">Change route priorities from floats to integers to fix the PHP deprecation warning "Implicit conversion from float to int loses precision"</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p>If you encounter any issues after updating, please open an <a href="https://github.com/nicumicle/simple-jwt-login/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="">issue</a> on GitHub.</p>]]></content>
